<L>__{exterior fort, west battery}
<A>__{tracking. french cannon fire rips into the fortifications, exploding wood and earth, shredding the english gun crew with cannister. the english fight stubbornly, but we feel they're outgunned. meanwhile ...}
<B>__{wide angle from the water}
<A>__{a new artillery duel erupts. the action is to the west side of the fort. on the north, the fire fight is reflected on the black water of lake george in our foreground. then a dark shape wiping to the right cuts off those reflections. we see in silhouette the outline of a birch canoe moving silently, barely rippling the mirrored surface of the lake.}
